Nigerians react to Korra’s sister video
Social media users have reacted differently to Korra’s sister’s video about the dancer’s marriage and her husband.
National Daily picked some of the comments, read below:
Amicableluxury:
“Online validation isn’t a healthy practice. You and your sisters need to get some rest off this space.”
Feyisayorichards:
“I thought we’ve moved on from this story.”
_Dunniadee:
“Everything I know about these people is against my will.”


